librbrntrvll documentation


PREREQUISITES
=============

You need the following packages in order to build this documentation:

	* xmlto
	* docbook
	* docbook-xml
	* docbook-xsl
	* docbook-xsl-doc-html

Additionally, you need those to edit diagrams:

	* dia


BUILDING
========

To build the documentation, just call make:

	$ make

The complete output structure will be in the "out" directory and
"out/index.html" is the HTML index. To clean it, call

	$ make clean

